# Environment Variables for Lords of Doomspire Simulation

# Anthropic API Key for Claude AI players
# Get your API key from: https://console.anthropic.com/
# Required when using claude player type (p1=claude, p2=claude, etc.)
ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=your_anthropic_api_key_here

# Setup Instructions:
# 1. Copy this file to .env in the same directory
# 2. Replace 'your_anthropic_api_key_here' with your actual API key
# 3. Save the file
# 4. You can now use claude players: node run-test.js --single-turn p1=claude 